gov.nih.ncats.molwitch.spi

Interface FingerprinterImpl


  • public interface FingerprinterImpl
    Interface that can generate fingerprints.

    All implementations of this interface should be placed in the src/main/resources/META-INF/services/gov.nih.ncats.chemkit.spi.FingerprinterImpl file so the ServiceLoader can find them.

    Author:
    katzelda

      • supports

        boolean supports(Fingerprinters.FingerprintSpecification options)
        Does this implementation support the given FingerPrinterOptions. If this implementation does, then true will be returned. This is used by
        Parameters:
        options - the FingerPrinterOptions to check which may include the name of the algorithm, any parameter settings.
        Returns:
        true if it does support it; false otherwise.

      • isDefault

        boolean isDefault()

        Returns:
        true if this is the default, false otherwise.
